{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_01_01",
  "title": "白石沙季",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時は遡り",
      "startTime": 0.3999999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月のテンペストがデビューしてしばらく経った頃",
      "startTime": 1.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3500.0000000000005,
          "startTime": 5.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshimi-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "……今日は{user}さんに\n物申したいことがあります",
      "startTime": 8.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ、沙季。そんな怖い顔して\n俺、何かやらかしたっけ……？",
      "startTime": 14.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、そうではありません",
      "startTime": 17.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんの日々の\nマネージメントは熱意に溢れています",
      "startTime": 21.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、配慮も行き届いていると思います",
      "startTime": 24.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに……いえ、だからこそ\n……もったいない",
      "startTime": 32.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "なぜ{user}さんは\n絶妙に締まりがなく、計画性に乏しいのですか？",
      "startTime": 35.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "月ストとサニピのグループ分けの時もそうでした\n唐突で、計画性を感じません",
      "startTime": 42.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "本当は素敵な提案なのに\nあのやり方では全然伝わりません",
      "startTime": 48.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "あのままうまく意図が伝わらなければ……",
      "startTime": 51.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "解散だってあり得たかもしれないんですよ？",
      "startTime": 55.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すまない……返す言葉がないよ",
      "startTime": 59.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "それに、そのあらゆるものが山積みにされた机です\n計画性のなさが滲み出ています",
      "startTime": 67.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "仕事用のデスクがこんな状態になるなんて……もうっ\n整理整頓という言葉をどこかに忘れてきたんですか",
      "startTime": 74.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、これは違うんだ。しばらく外出が多かったから\n書類がたまってしまって……",
      "startTime": 81.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "だとしても乱雑過ぎます。何事もまずは形から\n机を綺麗にして、仕事の仕方も綺麗にしていきましょう",
      "startTime": 89.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "言うのは簡単だけど……それが出来たら\nこうはなっていない訳で",
      "startTime": 96.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん？",
      "startTime": 99.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、ただお小言を言うだけではありません\n解決策だって用意してあります。この本をどうぞ",
      "startTime": 104.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "『人生を三角定規にする方法』……？",
      "startTime": 108.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "はい\nテレビでも紹介された、人生哲学の本です",
      "startTime": 113.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "規範を守り、きちっとした生活を送るための\n考え方や生活習慣のノウハウが書かれているんです",
      "startTime": 120.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "私も読んで、とても感銘を受けました\nこれを読めばきっと変わるはずです",
      "startTime": 127.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……意外と勉強になるかもしれないな\nよし、これを読んで明日から頑張るよ",
      "startTime": 134.74272521585226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ。分かってくれて嬉しいです\n{user}さん",
      "startTime": 140.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "あの……この間お貸しした本\nそろそろ返していただけますか？",
      "startTime": 146.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、あの本な。えっと、どこにやったっけ\n確かこの辺だと思うんだけど……",
      "startTime": 154.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……",
      "startTime": 158.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "私のお貸しした本は\n読んだはずですよね？",
      "startTime": 161.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、もちろん。一気に読み終えたよ\nとても勉強になった",
      "startTime": 166.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "それなのにどうしてこの体たらくなんですか？",
      "startTime": 168.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、その……頭で理解するのと、実際に行動を\n起こすのとの間には、大きな壁があってだな……",
      "startTime": 176.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……もういいです。本の力をもってしても\n改善しないなら、もう荒療治しかないのかも……",
      "startTime": 185.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski025.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n一つ提案があります",
      "startTime": 190.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski026.m4a",
      "text": "これからその机を片づけさせてくれますか？\n寮のお部屋の整理整頓も、私にやらせて欲しいんです",
      "startTime": 196.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　いや、そんな……\n事務所のアイドルにそんなことをさせる訳には……",
      "startTime": 203.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_01-ski027.m4a",
      "text": "それが嫌なら、自分でやるようにして下さい",
      "startTime": 207.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
